android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.ezsch.browser.activity.BrowserActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.title: KKDiscovery-Fast&Small Browser
playstore_details.description:
Small,fast,smart,KK Discovery is one of the best web browsers for Andriod.
Only 1M, the free small app size ensures your device keep running smoothly. KK Discovery provides users with fast web page viewing speed and much security. It ‘s also a very smart and small web browser with many funny HTML5 games and concise local homepages. 
Top Features
Smart Search
Faster Browsing Speed
Data Saving
ADBlock
Concise Homepage
Local Content
Night Mode
Incognito Browsing
H5 Game
Multi-languauge
Learn more about KKDiscovery:
•Smart Search: KK Browser with new version brings revolutionary innovation in the field of results display, which will show you the SERP across three main stream search engines that catches you best with richer information and more intuitive display for each piece of your search query.

•Small: Less than 1M RAM, three-second installing, zero-second-start, smooth use, slow speed wipe-out. 

•Local Content: Push you the local weather forecast and hot news&fun in real time.

•User-defined: Add any website to the navigation for quicker access from viewing history and bookmark. 

•AD BlockExcept for the perfect built-in one,the User-defined ad-block function is also provided for quicker pages loading and data saving.

•Data saving: Swift to no-pic mode for quicker pages loading in slow network without affecting browsing experience.

•Concise homepage: New design navigation page, one-click integration tool bar, and humanized bottom keys for fast and easy target content search.

•Safety: OS will not save your browsing records and will protect your privacy omni-directionally when using the non-trace browsing function.  

•Muti-language: 10 country languages support, such as English, Indonesian, Spanish, Norwegian, Portuguese, etc.

Your suggestion will be highly appreciated.Email us:zhuhaibing@joydream.cn
Follow KKDiscovery on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KKDiscovery-333489723699711/
To know more about us, please visit:http://www.joydream.cn
